---
const {
  scope = 'this page',
} = Astro.props;
---

{/* =========================
   EDITOR INSTRUCTIONS
   =========================

⚠️ IMPORTANT: Incorrect formatting can break the site.

DO NOT EDIT:
- The page title
- The page description
- Any import lines
- <HumanWrittenNotes />
- Section headings
- Section order
- The <BlogSection links={` line
- The closing `} />

ONLY EDIT:
- The link lines inside each BlogSection
- The *Last Updated* date for the section you changed

RULES:
- One link per line
- DO NOT use commas
- DO NOT wrap lines in quotes
- Format MUST be:
  url|Name|Description.|BADGE

EXAMPLES:
https://example.com|Example Site|Short description.
https://example.com|Example Site|Short description.|NEW
https://example.com|Example Site|Short description.|⭐
https://example.com|Example Site|Short description.|NLU
https://example.com|Example Site|Short description.|⭐|NEW

NOTES:
- ⭐ = featured (appears at top)
- NEW = manually added highlight
- NLU = pushed to bottom automatically
- You can combine badges: |⭐|NEW
- If unsure, copy an existing line and edit it

Please do not edit the headings or section structure for {scope}.

========================= */}